将 ShellTool 模式的保留输出字节上限翻倍，保留 FullBuffer 不设上限的现有行为；同时同步调整 `exec_tests` 中依赖旧上限/旧分配比例的断言，其余 FullBuffer 与不依赖旧上限语义的测试保持不变。

### EDIT 1
- file: `core/src/exec.rs`
- where: `ExecCapturePolicy` cap constant (~65) — 将 ShellTool 模式保留输出上限提高一倍，`retained_bytes_cap()` 会自动随常量生效，FullBuffer 仍走 `None`
```old
/// Hard cap on bytes retained from exec stdout/stderr/aggregated output.
///
/// This mirrors unified exec's output cap so a single runaway command cannot
/// OOM the process by dumping huge amounts of data to stdout/stderr.
const EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES: usize = DEFAULT_OUTPUT_BYTES_CAP;
```
```new
/// Hard cap on bytes retained from exec stdout/stderr/aggregated output.
///
/// Shell-tool capture keeps a bounded buffer that is intentionally larger than
/// the default per-stream process cap so long command output is truncated less
/// aggressively without becoming unbounded.
const EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES: usize = DEFAULT_OUTPUT_BYTES_CAP * 2;
```

### EDIT 2
- file: `core/src/exec_tests.rs`
- where: `aggregate_output_prefers_stderr_on_contention (~129)` — 该测试把旧的 1/3 vs 2/3 分配比例写死了；上限翻倍后应继续按生产逻辑验证“偏向 stderr”的当前比例，而不是依赖旧常量值
```old
    let aggregated = aggregate_output(&stdout, &stderr, Some(EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES));
    let stdout_cap = EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES / 3;
    let stderr_cap = EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES.saturating_sub(stdout_cap);

    assert_eq!(aggregated.text.len(), EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES);
    assert_eq!(aggregated.text[..stdout_cap], vec![b'a'; stdout_cap]);
    assert_eq!(aggregated.text[stdout_cap..], vec![b'b'; stderr_cap]);
```
```new
    let aggregated = aggregate_output(&stdout, &stderr, Some(EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES));
    let stdout_cap = EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES / 4;
    let stderr_cap = EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES.saturating_sub(stdout_cap);

    assert_eq!(aggregated.text.len(), EXEC_OUTPUT_MAX_BYTES);
    assert_eq!(aggregated.text[..stdout_cap], vec![b'a'; stdout_cap]);
    assert_eq!(aggregated.text[stdout_cap..], vec![b'b'; stderr_cap]);
```

